      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·唐風·003.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">揚之水.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>揚之水，不流束薪。彼其之子，不與我戍申。懷哉懷哉！曷月予還歸哉！
揚之水，不流束楚。彼其之子，不與我戍甫。懷哉懷哉！曷月予還歸哉！
揚之水，不流束蒲。彼其之子，不與我戍許。懷哉懷哉！曷月予還歸哉！</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Amidst the fretted waters,
The white rocks stand up grandly.
Bringing a robe of white silk, with a vermilion collar,
We will follow you to Yuh.
When we have seen the princely lord,
Shall we not rejoice?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
