      <prop type="x-translation-ref">揚之水.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>揚之水，不流束楚，終鮮兄弟，維予與女，無信人之言，人實迋女。
揚之水，不流束薪，終鮮兄弟，維予二人，無信人之言，人實不信！</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Amidst the fretted waters,
The white rocks stand glistening.
Bringing a robe of white silk, with a vermilion collar, and
We will follow you to Ivaou.
When we have seen the princely lord,
What sorrow will remain to us?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
