      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·唐風·003.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">揚之水.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>揚之水，白石鑿鑿，素衣朱襮，從子于沃，既見君子，云何不樂。
揚之水，白石皓皓，素衣朱繡，從子于鵠，既見君子，云何其憂。
揚之水，白石粼粼，我聞有命，不敢以告人！</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Amidst the fretted waters,
The white rocks clearly show.
We have heard your orders,
And will not dare to inform any one of them.</seg>
      </tuv>
